<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Not Authenticated</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>

<body class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-screen text-center px-4">

    <div class="w-full max-w-xs sm:max-w-sm">
        <img src="https://img.freepik.com/free-vector/angry-man-concept-illustration_114360-13127.jpg?t=st=1742413356~exp=1742416956~hmac=e47f4ba90cf7b09836794e455b4086aba8bd22118cab14ffddad1e49aeb44706&w=826"
            alt="Request Not Found" class="w-full h-auto mx-auto">
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-700 mt-6">Oops! Request Not Found</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-500 mt-2 text-sm sm:text-base">
        The token is either invalid or expired, or the user is not logged in.
    </p>

    <a href="/login-user"
        class="mt-6 bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-white px-5 py-3 rounded-lg shadow-md transition text-sm sm:text-base">
        Sign in to continue
    </a>

</body>

</html>